Poached, steamed, grilled or curried with the true essence and flavors of the beautiful Ashtamudi & Arabian sea intact. How about a dinner exclusively dedicated to this fresh bounty? Well, our mind reading has transpired into a ‘Seafood Night’ especially for you as part of the Chakara Season 2 series at The Raviz Ashtamudi.
